text: Akram Dashti is a Pakistani politician who has been a Member of the Senate of Pakistan, since March 2018. ==Political career== Dashti was elected to the Senate of Pakistan as a candidate of National Party on general seat from Balochistan in 2018 Pakistani Senate election. He took oath as Senator on 12 March 2018. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Members of the Senate of Pakistan
